### =====================
### POSTS
### =====================

### Create Post
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "media": [
    {
      "url": "https://picsum.photos/800/600",
      "type": "image",
      "altText": "Beautiful view"
    }
  ],
  "caption": "Amazing sunset at the beach! #sunset #beach #nature @janedoe",
  "visibility": "public"
}

### Get Post by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts/POST_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get User Posts
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts/user/USER_ID_HERE?page=1&limit=12
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get Posts by Hashtag
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts/hashtag/sunset?page=1&limit=12

### Get Trending Posts
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts/trending?page=1&limit=12

### Update Post
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/posts/POST_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "caption": "Updated caption! #updated",
  "commentsDisabled": false
}

### Delete Post
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/posts/POST_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Increment Post View
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts/POST_ID_HERE/view

